                            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Angra do Heroismo, Portugal</p>
                            <p><strong>Host School:</strong> Escola Basica Integrada de Angra do Heroismo</p>
                            <p><strong>Participants:</strong> Mrs. Pepa Pavlova, Mrs. Kalina Nikolova, Mrs. Annie Pavlova</p>
